# Hacker News UI Tests

This project contains automated UI tests for the Hacker News website using Playwright and Pytest.  
It verifies key features such as article sorting, navigation, and element presence to ensure a stable user experience.  

Tests are designed to be easy to extend and maintain, demonstrating skills in web automation and test design.

# CLI Tools

This folder contains scripts to run and manage test suites.

## run_hn_tests.py

- Runs the Hacker News UI tests located in `projects/hacker-news-ui-tests/`.
- Usage:

```bash
python automated-ui-sorting-check.py
